              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Blog A: daily posts (5/week). Avg read time: 47 seconds. Blog B: weekly deep dives. Avg read time: 1:38. Quality over frequency. Readers value substance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile readers abandon 57% faster</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Desktop reader: 2:31 avg time on article. Mobile reader: 1:05 avg time. Same article. Mobile reading = skimming. Write for scannability.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-amber-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
